{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meet the KEVIN! Hoover Heroes Demo is a physics-based multiplayer party game that can be played online with up to 8 players, where Kevin and his friends create chaos with their vacuums while cleaning.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3453620/extras/gif_j\u0131ggly_cleaners.gif?t=1739108667\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Start the fight with Kevin's vacuum cleaner that he never leaves behind. Team up or play solo! Control Kevin the &quot;cleaner&quot; and his team. Each one is waiting for you with their jiggly bellies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3453620/extras/gif_perfect_vacuum.gif?t=1739108667\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use Kevin's superior vacuum cleaner to pull even the largest objects and fill them in his bag. Then use them to throw them at your opponents and eliminate them!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3453620/extras/gif_classic_mode.gif?t=1739108667\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hoover Heroes has a game play based on fun and chaos. The cleaners try to knock each other down with their throws, slaps and more to eliminate &quot;co-workers&quot; and earn points! Be the last KEVIN standing to earn some extra!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3453620/extras/gif_unyielding_power.gif?t=1739108667\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No matter how many times Kevin falls down, he always knows how to get back up. Avoid the objects thrown by your opponents. You may fall to the ground when you get a hit. But Kevin's endless energy will help you get back up!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3453620/extras/gif_kevins.gif?t=1739108667\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Even though Kevin is a &quot;professional&quot;, he can get bored cleaning alone. Invite your friends over and try it together. Become a team of 2, 4 or 8 and enjoy the chaos!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3453620/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739108667","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3453620/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739108667","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3453620/24d2e4703bc85a659daa07d325235acf60f8e2a3/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739108667","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3453620/24d2e4703bc85a659daa07d325235acf60f8e2a3/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739108667","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Game demo","id":10}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meet the KEVIN! Hoover Heroes Demo is a physics-based multiplayer party game that can be played online with up to 8 players, where Kevin and his friends create chaos with their vacuums while cleaning.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3453620/extras/gif_j\u0131ggly_cleaners.gif?t=1739108667\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Start the fight with Kevin's vacuum cleaner that he never leaves behind. Team up or play solo! Control Kevin the &quot;cleaner&quot; and his team. Each one is waiting for you with their jiggly bellies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3453620/extras/gif_perfect_vacuum.gif?t=1739108667\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use Kevin's superior vacuum cleaner to pull even the largest o